                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18220417-199-off1042 t18220417-199-crimeloc1044"></join>. These shirts were in the drying' ground, which is not fenced all round. They were stolen on Wednesday, the 20th of March, between two and three o'clock; they had been hanging out for an hour before.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18220417-199-person1829">
                  EDWARD 
                  VASS
               <interp inst="t18220417-199-person1829" type="surname" value="VASS"></interp>
