                     <interp inst="t18220417-199-person1829" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am pot-boy at the Compasses, Hornsey. I saw the prisoner take two shirts off the line, and put them in his pocket. I told my mistress. Howard pursued and took him with the shirts.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18220417-199-person1830">
                  JOHN 
                  HOWARD
               <interp inst="t18220417-199-person1830" type="surname" value="HOWARD"></interp>
